atkinson                Atkinson's inequality index
clean.income            Utility functions
eqscale                 Transform an incdist object with an
                        equivalence scale
fgt                     The Foster Greer Thorbecke poverty index
fields                  Fields mobility index
ge                      Generalized entropy inequality index
gini                    Generalized gini or concentration coefficient
hasse                   A Hasse doagram of an inequalioty or poverty ordering
incdist                 An income distribution object
kolm                    Kolm's inequality index
lorenz                  Estimate a generalized lorenz curve
plot.lorenz             Plot a Lorenz curve
plot.tip                Plot a TIP or CPG curve
prospect                Prospect theory welfare index
tip                     The "three I's of poverty" (TIP) or "Cumulated
                        Poverty Gap" (CGP) curve
